{"tid":1185104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國駐港總領事館貼文悼念　形容六四是「大屠殺」","createTime":"2019-06-04T05:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T00:04:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":864,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"68b04d3d3e0be41bc585eb96a3ef8fbe17c58cb4","tid":1185104,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:18:07.000Z","msg":"今日（4日）是六四事件30年，德國駐港總領事館在社交網站fb貼文悼念，稱「今日是天安門大屠殺的30周年。這個日子讓我們銘記永遠不將人權和自由視為理所當然」。<br />\n<br />\n德國駐港總領事館發布這則簡短帖文後，不少網民回應，其中「Brian Lowah」表示感謝（Thanks）；Wendy Yan對此表示讚賞（Really appreciated）；更有網民「Hang Wong」呼籲港人在6月9日（下周日）反《逃犯條例》修訂遊行要加油（Hong Kong people fight on 9 jun）等。"},{"pid":"ef5c386960552e2269f7a7b87748ceb945500b41","tid":1185104,"uid":140802,"like":507,"dislike":4,"score":503,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:19:44.000Z","msg":"愈來愈鐘意德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6a966e33e639c82a80a4166dcdd9bd3f67fd55","tid":1185104,"uid":73381,"like":330,"dislike":3,"score":327,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:20:39.000Z","msg":"近排咁搶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8babdfdd7172dd1acb6833653e25ddd867020928","tid":1185104,"uid":254371,"like":11,"dislike":340,"score":-329,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:21:04.000Z","msg":"班左膠出少句聲啦"},{"pid":"c9635e80dd78cd490fa5e00a08d1bdb5a53d8ce4","tid":1185104,"uid":63154,"like":449,"dislike":6,"score":443,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:21:56.000Z","msg":"德國自己都犯過呢種大錯，講嘢好有份量架"},{"pid":"159ac41bd2210c7a3e234d68a3f8a79d48f9789c","tid":1185104,"uid":38651,"like":190,"dislike":0,"score":190,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:22:51.000Z","msg":"往年都唔覺有咁多國家出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c358be0d0c9df4c3d7c63c1332f56e6afa0b980d","tid":1185104,"uid":244332,"like":357,"dislike":1,"score":356,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.